        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <title>Details</title>
            <dl outputclass="since">
            <dlentry props="native">
                <dt>Since</dt>
                <dd>v4.2.0</dd>
            </dlentry>
            </dl>
            <p>When you do not need to record any audio and video streams, you can call this method to destroy the recording object. Before you call this method, if you are recording a media stream, you need to call <xref keyref="stopRecording" /> to stop recording.</p>
        </section>
